#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Cāpālavagga"
msgstr "1. At the Cāpāla Shrine"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Nibbidāsutta"
msgstr "4. Disillusionment"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.4:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Cattārome, bhikkhave, iddhipādā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ekantanibbidāya virāgāya "
"nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these four bases of psychic power, when developed and "
"cultivated, lead solely to disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, "
"insight, awakening, and extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn51.4:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn51.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ "
"iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.4:1.4"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "energy …"

msgctxt "sn51.4:1.5"
msgid "cittasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "mental development …"

msgctxt "sn51.4:1.6"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.4:1.7"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro iddhipādā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ekantanibbidāya "
"virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"These four bases of psychic power, when developed and cultivated, lead "
"solely to disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, insight, awakening, "
"and extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.4:1.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
